{"tid":1912201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息人士指習近平擬前往武漢視察","createTime":"2020-03-06T01:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T05:52:51.000Z","uid":212626,"like":149,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"f914bfe2846a80ff09e2cab0cbe0b269660c775d","tid":1912201,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情近日有所緩和，本報獲悉，國家主席習近平計劃近期赴疫情最先爆發及最嚴重的湖北武漢視察。一直坐鎮前線的國務院副總理孫春蘭，<span style=\"color: red;\">昨日率領中央指導組到社區考察，其間有多名住戶在樓上大叫「假的，假的」</span>，抗議物業管理公司及基層幹部為應付領導「做騷」，孫春蘭立即要求調查事件，強調杜絕形式主義、官僚主義。<br />\n<br />\n北京消息人士對本報稱，習近平擬於近期前往湖北武漢視察新冠疫情防控工作。習近平1月28日在北京會見世衛總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）時稱，「這一次的疫情防控工作，我一直是在親自指揮、親自部署」，但他僅於上月10日和本月2日，分別在北京的社區和科研機構考察，其餘與防疫工作相關的公開行程均不屬第一線。<br />\n<br />\n為防意外 習料慰問警察公僕社區<br />\n消息人士稱，雖然中央尚未確定疫情轉捩點已到，但疫情傳播已有所緩和後，習近平料於近期親臨武漢。<span style=\"color: red;\">他稱，習近平料將抵達最先收治患者的金銀潭醫院考察，包括武漢版「小湯山」的火神山醫院、雷神山醫院也是行程之一</span>。此外，習近平也將進入社區慰問武漢當地居民。知情者表示，中國科學院武漢病毒研究所以及百步亭社區也是計劃行程，但為防止意外狀况，官方將選擇安排如警察社區或公務員社區。<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，擔任中央領導小組組長的國務院總理李克強，1月27日「受習近平委託」到武漢考察指導防疫工作；擔任中央指導組組長的副總理孫春蘭，自1月22日起長駐武漢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200306/s00013/1583433532578/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200306%2Fs00013%2F1583433532578%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a359596c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200306%2Fs00013%2F1583433532578%2F&h=186dd1ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200306/s00013/1583433532578/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49eb77e9dc4535bbdb59c52d45c0b9ad5ce9e5fa","tid":1912201,"uid":74778,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:39:40.000Z","msg":"當地有勇武未"},{"pid":"94ef23b0af906a203d490785e140c202a963ac7f","tid":1912201,"uid":212626,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"刁总去醫院<br />\n奶刁柒婆應該會跟住做擦佢鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb63029d1f565eb76ac25ba8710e20d2f3d44159","tid":1912201,"uid":550,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"49eb77e9dc4535bbdb59c52d45c0b9ad5ce9e5fa","tid":1912201,"uid":74778,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:39:40.000Z","msg":"當地有勇武未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"武漢佬百萬雄師嗰陣香港人仲發緊夢"},{"pid":"21d65783c3e6cdd95729972f9d01c372ab8c7a2e","tid":1912201,"uid":226955,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:42:55.000Z","msg":"習近平<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">替身</span>擬前往武漢視察"},{"pid":"12ceb03386df178f6a9f0b22f656679049e33f70","tid":1912201,"uid":277339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:43:34.000Z","msg":"全支共，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fdf7d65e965aa25eb3539e0b3478d92e95eac3","tid":1912201,"uid":141419,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:50:39.000Z","msg":"中共將成為歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2014cf4ffd24348c2f10166cf42d8974dd988d19","tid":1912201,"uid":249160,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"親自視察嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c8ed3a0c9f9dc68327ad485a26315efc7e6c78","tid":1912201,"uid":184679,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201808/987b05e43bee9e4f9384d4a5f1554af8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201808%2F987b05e43bee9e4f9384d4a5f1554af8.JPG&h=0fad1