親自指揮、親自部署」，但他僅於上月10日和本月2日，分別在北京的社區和科研機構考察，其餘與防疫工作相關的公開行程均不屬第一線。<br />\n<br />\n為防意外 習料慰問警察公僕社區<br />\n消息人士稱，雖然中央尚未確定疫情轉捩點已到，但疫情傳播已有所緩和後，習近平料於近期親臨武漢。<span style=\"color: red;\">他稱，習近平料將抵達最先收治患者的金銀潭醫院考察，包括武漢版「小湯山」的火神山醫院、雷神山醫院也是行程之一</span>。此外，習近平也將進入社區慰問武漢當地居民。知情者表示，中國科學院武漢病毒研究所以及百步亭社區也是計劃行程，但為防止意外狀况，官方將選擇安排如警察社區或公務員社區。<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，擔任中央領導小組組長的國務院總理李克強，1月27日「受習近平委託」到武漢考察指導防疫工作；擔任中央指導組組長的副總理孫春蘭，自1月22日起長駐武漢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200306/s00013/1583433532578/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200306%2Fs00013%2F1583433532578%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a359596c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200306%2Fs00013%2F1583433532578%2F&h=186dd1ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200306/s00013/1583433532578/</a><br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次派Model幾去？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c90f2935627f8688e59ec73faaea0f22a6bd61a1","tid":1912201,"uid":199957,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"49eb77e9dc4535bbdb59c52d45c0b9ad5ce9e5fa","tid":1912201,"uid":74778,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:39:40.000Z","msg":"當地有勇武未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"叫假的假的果班已經係 而家應該全部火化哂了"},{"pid":"2c6505219d2e9d372c16a2b2a47678625e5b158c","tid":1912201,"uid":67771,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4b4d1aa74e5caa2d30b7de1d370c91608083cd35","tid":1912201,"uid":189109,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"bc74d8c8f1dc28395572a0bc58ba33a